      "author": "prncc",
      "description": "This release lets you easily add the `repeat` field to notes. Toggle on \"Enqueue non-repeating notes\" in settings and notes without a repeat field will show up at the end of the queue, sorted by file creation time (oldest to newest). Repeat options are taken from the default repeat period, and a special \"never\" repeat option is added (so that the note you're looking at stops appearing in the queue).",
